name: When AI Goes Bad
description:
when ai goes bad...
building a future world brimming with artificial intelligence, but here in the present most of us are still trying to figure out what AI even is. “what is the nature of creativity?” and “how do we define consciousness?” Posing the question “how can I understand AI?” is nearly as daunting as asking “what is the meaning of life?”

In this NFT, it depicts what happens when AI goes bad or does it? Or was it all a dream? Watch, see, listen and learn until the end. 

I know its a 2:30 NFT  but give yourself the time to enjoy this
